title: Rubber Spatula in Red
description: The Rubbermaid Commercial High Heat Spatula is an all-purpose scraper ideal for use in any industrial-size kitchen. This rubber spatula has a red nylon handle with white silicone blade. The scraper resists heat up to 500°F (260°Celsius) and is stain resistant and will not scratch cookware. The spatula measures 16-1/2 in. and is commercial dishwasher safe. This rubber spatula is certified to National Sanitation Foundation (NSF) standards for food safety.
